HEADWORD: Prophetical
<hw>Pro*phet"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr> }</mhw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>propheticus</ets>, Gr.
<?/: cf. F. <ets>proph⟦eacute⟧tique</ets>.]</ety> <def>Containing, or
